headline: Analysts Reassess Oracle Corporation (ORCL)’s Long-Term Prospects
summary: Oracle Corp (NYSE:ORCL) is one of the stocks with huge growth potential, according to the media. On January 23, Morgan Stanley cut Oracle Corp (NYSE:ORCL)’s price target to $213 from $320 while reiterating an Equal-weight rating, warning that the company’s GPU-as-a-service expansion poses “little room for error” amid rising capital needs, funding pressures, and a […]
